 "\n(a) Determine and interpret the marginal distributions of both X and Y .\n\
(b) Calculate the 75 % quantile for the marginal distribution of Y .\n(c) \
Determine and interpret the conditional distribution of satisfaction level \
for X =1.\n(d) Are the two variables independent?\n(e) Calculate and \
interpret the covariance of X and Y ."
}], "Subsubsection",
